      <title>随着特朗普的贸易战权重，法国的增长前景消失了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/france-s-growth-outlook-fades-as-trump-s-trade-war-weighs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该国中央银行说，随着全球贸易战的预期影响使本年度的开始已经很慢，法国的经济前景已经恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/france-s-growth-outlook-fades-as-trump-s-trade-war-weighs</guid>
